    <p class="location">Suwon, South Korea</p>
    <div class="links">
      <a href="https://github.com/KYBee" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a>
      <a href="https://nullnull.tistory.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Blog</a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/kybee/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn</a>
